## 🚀 Dependencies

### New Dependencies
- Threshold signature libraries (BLS, Schnorr)
- Light client verification libraries

### Updated Dependencies
- Blockchain node v0.7.1+
- Bridge service v0.7.1+

## 🔐 Security Considerations

- **External security audit required before merge**
- Multi-sig threshold must be set conservatively (recommend 3-of-5 minimum)
- Time-lock periods must account for chain reorg depth
- Validator key management must use HSM or secure enclaves
- Audit trail must be tamper-evident and exportable
- Emergency pause must require multi-sig (no single-key override)

